{"tid":2193913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新股IPO】樂享互動","createTime":"2020-09-08T07:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T16:23:23.000Z","uid":364894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8293f71ca657f77c40e7b0b2e33061c7a8bc7d","tid":2193913,"uid":364894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"又有新股抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樂享互動已通過上市聆訊，據外電報道指，樂享互動計劃集資2億美元（約15.6億港元），樂享互動已開始投資者路演，並於9月10日（本周四）建薄。樂享互動於2008年成立，是一間媒體營銷服務商，為行業客戶分析及分銷的產品，並提供效果類營銷服務，幫助行業客戶獲得用戶。聯席保薦人為中信建投、招商及交銀。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月底， 集團建立的應用組合覆蓋超過十個種類（如遊戲、視頻及工具應用）；集團的網絡文學產品包括覆蓋69個文學類別的681多冊網絡書籍；而集團的Html 5遊戲產品包括超過 157個覆蓋RPG、戰略、動作及冒險種類的Html 5遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年3月底，集團溢利按年增91.9%至2051萬元（人民幣，下同）；收入按年增71.5%至1.67億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2746028/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%AB%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%8715.6%E5%84%84%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2746028%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2582%25A1IPO%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%258715.6%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=a938e933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2746028/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%AB%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%8715.6%E5%84%84%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"7c0c5061be248c82cc0c2ee951ca5f508f9cf1a9","tid":2193913,"uid":19322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"知唔知一手幾個多股<br />\n<br />\n好似好少貨<img src=\"/